{
  "stem": "747.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all of the sudden, we hear a big noise, and peeked out in the window.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We saw that, by the fence, these guys, the sonderkommando with axe and with shovel, they're banging on the fence.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the fence is falling down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we just-- we were just stunned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We looked at each other, and a minute, later there was a big flame came out from the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We fell on our stomach.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was shaking like a leaf, and didn't dare to look.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And by that time, the Nazis were shooting and yelling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I started to run around, and men were running.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they who were working, side-- it was a field, they were working there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when they saw something going on, they started to run.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I understand one person made it, then ran away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But the rest were shot, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then where we were lying there, shaking, all of the sudden an SS came up, and was surprised to see what are you doing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were trying to explain that we are cleaning the towers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we took us in right away, made the 20 girls in a kommando, and marched to the-- and we had to go through the big gate where was their office building.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And our leader had to give the-- the-- the order that 20 girls in-- and what they were working.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he's taking them back to their-- to their sleeping quarters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we heard as the head of the SS-- SS said, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They saw too much, they have to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- we were sure that this is the end of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "About a day or two, we stayed in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know much what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
